high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter, turn left, go forward, turn left at the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Move a bit to the left
Cut the apple on the table
Put the knife on the table
Pick up an apple piece
Move around the table and go to the microwave
Put the apple piece in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the apple piece
Turn around,go forward, turn left at the table
Put the apple piece on the table
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple and cook a piece

high_descs: Turn and go to the round table.
Pick up a knife on the table.
Turn and go to the round table.
Cut a tomato on the round table.
Put the knife on the round table.
Pick up a slice of apple on the round table.
Turn and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of apple in the microwave.
Turn and go to the round table.
Put the slice of apple on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the gray round table on the side near the wall and the refrigerator.
Pick up the gray knife under the spoon on the table.
Move over left towards the center of the table.
Cut the apple on the table on the left side of the potato into three parts.
Place the knife on the table in front of the apple.
Pick up one piece of the apple.
Turn left and go to the front of the microwave on the other side of the kitchen.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the gray round table.
Place the apple on the table on the right of the gray knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple on the table.
